  <description>
      <p>DOOM BFA is a DOOM 3: BFG Edition source port Based on RBDoom3BFG.</p>
      <p>This is the Special Flatpak Edition</p>
      <p>It contains all the features of the original with some UX extras for Flatpak</p>
      <p>The engine search for the game folder on your system.
      If the engine boots with the wrong game files, use the launch argument +set fs_basepath to set right game folder</p>
      <p>To install Open platform put the Open Platform .so file on either the game's or the save folder's (~/.var/app/io.github.maddecoder.Classic-RBDOOM-3-BFG/data/.doombfa) base folder.
        And the companion .so file on the ~/.var/app/io.github.maddecoder.Classic-RBDOOM-3-BFG/data/.doombfa/base/lib folder along side with any additional file that is required</p>
      <p>Known Bugs:</p>
      <p>(NOTE: Those bugs only apply to that release)</p>
      <ul style="list-style-type:none;">
        <li>Using Open Platform with Steam might result the associated game to be stuck in playing state,
         as a workaround restart the Steam Client</li>
        <li>The engine doesn't boot after installing OpenPlatform with Steam. Try to block access to the wayland socket from the app's flatpak rights</li>
        <li>Loading mods with custom new game entry might not load the custom new game entry. Restart the engine</li>
      </ul>
  </description>
